OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780423900
OL,3,CFootball and Rugby League stars begin
OL,4,C350 mile walk for Motor Neurone Disease
OL,6,FA group of football and rugby league
OL,7,Fstars have started a six day charity
OL,8,Fwalk for Motor Neurone Disease.
OL,10,FThe 'March of the Day' event involves
OL,11,Fa 340 mile walk, visiting 45 football
OL,12,Fand rugby grounds in support of the
OL,13,FDarby Rimmer MND Foundation.
OL,15,FThe charity was set up by former
OL,16,FLiverpool player Stephen Darby after
OL,17,Fhe was diagnosed with MND in 2018.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
