FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780423900
OL,3,CFootball and Rugby League stars begin
OL,4,C350 mile walk for Motor Neurone Disease
OL,6,FFormer England and Manchester City
OL,7,Fcaptain Steph Houghton - who married
OL,8,FStephen in 2018 - said: "It's just
OL,9,Famazing how many people have supported
OL,10,Fthe foundation over the last 6/7 years.
OL,12,F"Even today just to see the people
OL,13,Fturned up to walk just to get that
OL,14,Fawareness out there. We're very proud
OL,15,Fof what Chris and Stephen have
OL,16,Fcreated, it's just overwhelming every
OL,17,Ftime we do something like this."
OL,19,FTwo core teams will cover the entire
OL,20,Fwalk, with small teams signed up
OL,21,Fjoining for specific stages.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
