PN,39803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780423900
OL,3,CFootball and Rugby League stars begin
OL,4,C350 mile walk for Motor Neurone Disease
OL,6,FOver 1000 people are expected to take
OL,7,Fpart, including 100 former football
OL,8,Fand rugby league players.
OL,10,FEx-Liverpool and Wigan goalkeeper
OL,11,FChris Kirkland is one of the former
OL,12,Fplayers taking part.
OL,14,FHe said: "You look at people that are
OL,15,Fsuffering with MND and their families,
OL,16,Fthere needs to be more done.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780423900
OL,3,CFootball and Rugby League stars begin
OL,4,C350 mile walk for Motor Neurone Disease
OL,6,F"That only happens when people want to
OL,7,Fdo that, and the people that organise
OL,8,Fthese events are worth their weight in
OL,9,Fgold because they want to do something
OL,10,Fabout it, and the people that come and
OL,11,Fsupport it deserve a round of applause.
OL,13,F"A lot of people talk a good game
OL,14,Fsometimes and say they're going to
OL,15,Fthis and that but today is proof in
OL,16,Fthe pudding that everyone's behind
OL,17,Fthis and it's an incredible event."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
