FL,399,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780423900
OL,3,CFootball and Rugby League stars begin
OL,4,C350 mile walk for Motor Neurone Disease
OL,6,FThe previous two March of the Day
OL,7,Fevents in 2024 and 2025 raised over
OL,8,F#370,000, and were both three-day
OL,9,Fevents of over 180 miles, making the
OL,10,F2026 one the biggest-yet.
OL,12,FLiverpool legend David Fairclough also
OL,13,Fattended to support the event.
OL,15,FHe said: "Having known Stephen as a
OL,16,Fyoung lad, he was a pleasant lad, he
OL,17,Fwas always a kid who you wanted to
OL,18,Fsucceed a football so on a personal
OL,19,Fnote I'm very much supporting Stephen.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
