PN,39806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F398A1780423900
OL,3,CFootball and Rugby League stars begin
OL,4,C350 mile walk for Motor Neurone Disease
OL,6,F"It's an incredible thing and I think
OL,7,Fwe're only happy to support sports
OL,8,Fpeople who have MND."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
